prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D botanical illustration of a humorous birthday card for Lao Lao, from the perspective of her dog. Centered in the scene, Lao Lao (person on the left from photo) and Jordan (person on the right from photo, representing the dog) are illustrated as cartoon characters sitting on a colorful beach towel on a sandy beach. Lao Lao is laughing joyfully as Jordan playfully tries to lick her face. Lao Lao is wearing a light blue sweatshirt and black pants. Jordan is wearing a tan hoodie and dark maroon pants. Between them on the towel is a huge, slightly-chewed birthday cake decorated with paw prints and dog bone-shaped candles. In the foreground, a comical thought bubble emanates from Jordan's head containing a drawing of a dog wearing a party hat. The background shows gentle blue ocean waves and a clear sky. The entire scene is framed by a beautiful, whimsical border of lush tropical botanicals like monstera leaves, hibiscus flowers, and palm fronds in soft, natural colors. Centered in the middle of the design, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!". Full shot, bright and cheerful lighting, clean lines, vibrant color palette.
